'''Sociolinguistic research in [[India]]''' is research done in a society with the emphasis on linguistic situation.

[[India]] is a highly multilingual nation, where there are many languages spoken. Many people study for their [[PHD]] by doing this research but only a few have concentrated on the sociolinguistic situation of India. There are also other people who do research for community development.

